      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/156/22",
      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ زِيَارَةِ قَبْرِ أَبِي اَلْحَسَنِ مُوسَى بْنِ جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِمَا اَلسَّلاَمُ مِثْلُ زِيَارَةِ اَلْحُسَيْنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ قَالَ «نَعَمْ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3180 - It is narrated from Al-Hasan ibn Ali al-Washsha’ that he asked Abu al-Hasan al-Ridha (as) about the visitation of the grave of Abu al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) and whether it is similar to the visitation of Husayn (as), peace be upon him.\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes.\""
        ]
      }
    },
